  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Recruitment Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Highlights</strong></p>\n<p>We are looking for a self motivated, independent <strong>Recruitment Executive</strong> to join our growing team. If you are a people-oriented individual with strong communication skills and time management skills and are looking for a meaningful job in healthcare-related industry, we would like to invite you to consider joining our team.</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Positive work culture with a young an dynamic team</li>\n  <li>Located right above Kent Ridge MRT station</li>\n  <li>Meaningful job - you would be helping families recruit and screen for suitable caregivers</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>What does this Job Offer you?</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>5-day work week, office hours, 9:30AM – 6:30PM, Rest day on one weekday and one Saturday / Sunday.</strong></li>\n  <li>Job satisfaction. Through your work, you will provide families with qualified caregivers and trained helpers to look after the elderly or persons with disabilities.</li>\n  <li><strong>Mentorship, training and coaching will be provided.</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p>\n<p>As a <strong>Recruitment / HR Admin Executive</strong>, you will be tasked with the end-to-end recruitment of caregivers and helpers including:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Caregiver shortlisting, interview, selection and creation of biodata</li>\n  <li>Caregiver work permit and related processing</li>\n  <li>Onboarding, orientation and training</li>\n  <li>Integration counselling and post placement follow-up calls</li>\n  <li>Maintain social media page</li>\n  <li>Other ad hoc operational matters</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Open to applicants with no experience</li>\n  <li><strong>CEI holder (preferred) or Willing to train and pass the Certificate of Employment Intermediaries (Basic) before starting your job. Company will sponsor training and exam fee.</strong></li>\n  <li>Minimum diploma in any discipline.</li>\n  <li>At least 2 years in deskbound work in any field in Singapore.</li>\n  <li>Able to work independently with little supervision</li>\n  <li>Competent in spoken and written English.</li>\n  <li>Ability to converse Bahasa Indonesia / Melayu to our MDWs is not mandatory but would be helpful in performing the job.</li>\n  <li>Proficient with MS Word and Excel.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Work location: Kent Ridge MRT Station</li>\n  <li>14 days of annual leave</li>\n  <li>Birthday leave</li>\n  <li>Choice day leave</li>\n  <li>Performance bonus</li>\n  <li>Yearly bonus</li>\n  <li>Medical &amp; Dental Reimbursements</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Salary will commensurate with experience. We regret that only shortlisted applicants will be notified.</p>",
